3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper presents an end-to-end model for SRL, which involves machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of neural networks for SRL. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may involve the use of visual information for SRL.
